data.title: Reserve a Tee Time
data.meta_description: Whether you’re an NCGA member or a valued guest, we welcome you to experience our award-winning golf course and amenities.
data.text:
Poppy Hills tee times can be booked online up to 90 days in advance. If you’d like to book as a single player, please call the Golf Shop at (831) 622-8239.

Please review our Poppy Hills Golf Course Policies prior to booking.

*NCGA members are required to login with their Digital Profile or create a new login credential to access member tee times online at Poppy Hills. See detailed instructions.

From corporate events to weekend competitions, Poppy Hills is a great place to host group golf outings.

If your group consists of 16 or more players, you can gain booking access in advance of the usual 90-day booking window.

Please contact our Group Ambassador, Cassidy Young, at cyoung@ncga.org, or call the Golf Shop at (831) 622-8239 to begin the booking process.
